divs: Sighting Detailsi was standing outside looking for the space station and i thought i had found it until it started flashing red, blue, green yellow white. I went inside to get a camera and when i got back outside there was about two more and the first was bigger and brighter and flashing faster. we looked at them for about 30 min and they hadn't moved at all.
